NASA.

23:53.232 --> 23:58.837 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT BIGELOW: When I saw that
architecture
and that whole idea, I was
enchanted by that

23:58.871 --> 24:04.209 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
