something that
really looks cool and seems to
have a lot

24:04.243 --> 24:06.145 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of value.

24:06.178 --> 24:11.617 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: In 2006 and 2007,
Bigelow successfully
deployed two expandable
structures slightly

24:11.650 --> 24:17.556 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
